{"tid":2012986,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平的民族復興是蒙古族復興？","createTime":"2020-05-12T04:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T05:08:46.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"929e18af0d58212da04764a053befba63bdbbf12","tid":2012986,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:23:23.000Z","msg":"文 : 林保華<br />\n<br />\n五年前我在開始寫《我的雜種人生》回憶錄時，因為觸及我的漢蒙滿血統中博爾濟吉特氏的蒙族血統，曾與中國一位蒙族朋友交談。 他為多一位「族友」而高興，並且對我說：「我們當中好多人都知道習近平也是蒙族。」這話把我嚇了一跳，後來考察一些事件，似乎習近平本人也可能知道這一點。 他的臉形，尤其鼻子，是不是挺像成吉思汗啊？ 他陝西富平的老家離內蒙古也沒多少距離...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200512/5KOA7WXHQT5RBPIUOKYYCNUAZI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200512%2F5KOA7WXHQT5RBPIUOKYYCNUAZI%2F&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HSDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=fd979b97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200512%2F5KOA7WXHQT5RBPIUOKYYCNUAZI%2F&h=12ecda39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200512/5KOA7WXHQT5RBPIUOKYYCNUAZI/</a>"},{"pid":"92b59521af8a8092176d3d9f301635ad9f77836f","tid":2012986,"uid":228894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:36:16.000Z","msg":"華人世界基本上已經冇哂純種漢人"},{"pid":"e052cd3f060a8e65764e976ec2ccc0f46b42a80a","tid":2012986,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"92b59521af8a8092176d3d9f301635ad9f77836f","tid":2012986,"uid":228894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:36:16.000Z","msg":"華人世界基本上已經冇哂純種漢人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:40:38.000Z","msg":"孫權, 仲謀, &ldquo;碧目紫髯&rdquo; (藍眼睛紫鬍子)"},{"pid":"a333ab603577ffaa0f2de5a717ea9b77356b8d53","tid":2012986,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:41:09.000Z","msg":"驅逐韃虜&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"aa8159168325ae469b69d02c6cd1490344ed1a7f","tid":2012986,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1